            <title>中国 App Store 成人软件登下载榜榜首，伪装成学习 App + 无设定年龄限制</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/09/apple-app-store-porn-app-pretends-to-be-learning-app/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-app-store-porn-app-pretends-to-be-learning-app</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/09/apple-app-store-porn-app-pretends-to-be-learning-app/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 09 Oct 2023 09:05:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1198070</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>据中国媒体 IT 之家报道，Apple App Store 日前下架了一款登上免费榜首的「学习英文字母」 App，因为其本身原来竟是一款成人软件。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198078" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/4702-9ebe97d2873ac20bddf4482f64330042-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/4702-9ebe97d2873ac20bddf4482f64330042-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/4702-9ebe97d2873ac20bddf4482f64330042-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/4702-9ebe97d2873ac20bddf4482f64330042-scaled.jpg 738w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/4702-9ebe97d2873ac20bddf4482f64330042-709x1536.jpg 709w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/mobile/n/n/2023-10-08/doc-imzqhwff9971785.shtml">新浪</a></p><p>据 IT 之家报道，涉事软件没有年龄限制，分级属 4 岁以上。IT 之家表示，该款成人软件伪装成英文字母学习软件，但实际上会向用户提供赌博、色情网站的资讯和连结。IT 之家访问了其中一名用家小同，其表示本身下载这款软件是为了学习英文字母，但下载后发现这款软件「挂羊头卖狗肉」，实际上是一个提供色情资讯的软件。小同认为这种以学习软件为幌子的色情软件很容易对小朋友造成不良影响，非常危险。IT 之家经已就事件向 Apple 查询，Apple 方面回应指已经向 App 审核团队反映。</p><p>IT 之家亦发现 Apple 免费榜首再出现伪装成正经骑单车软件的成人软件，同样亦不设年龄限制。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198089" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/1e93-fbea93344e7031bc61d63492166a6eb8-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/1e93-fbea93344e7031bc61d63492166a6eb8-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/1e93-fbea93344e7031bc61d63492166a6eb8-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/1e93-fbea93344e7031bc61d63492166a6eb8-scaled.jpg 738w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/1e93-fbea93344e7031bc61d63492166a6eb8-709x1536.jpg 709w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/723/418.htm">IT 之家</a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198090" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/69ef-b68d394a29348291d1ef9b6207709d36-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/69ef-b68d394a29348291d1ef9b6207709d36-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/69ef-b68d394a29348291d1ef9b6207709d36-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/69ef-b68d394a29348291d1ef9b6207709d36-scaled.jpg 738w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/69ef-b68d394a29348291d1ef9b6207709d36-709x1536.jpg 709w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/723/418.htm">IT 之家</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/mobile/n/n/2023-10-08/doc-imzqhwff9971785.shtml">新浪</a>、<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/723/418.htm">IT 之家</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
